{
  "stem": "26111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the time that it gets to you, it's, you know, it's a different story.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, not that I can recall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were one or two.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were all in the railway uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The, the railway officials and railway employees had uniforms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody had uniforms in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, this was definitely-- so this was a-- it was chartered, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had to be paid for.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but, but it was done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- it's a miracle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Amazing, an amazing job that these people did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I would say, best of my recollection, maybe eight hours, maybe a little more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were stops.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We weren't the most urgent cargo that the, that the German trains were-- according to their lights-- that they were ferrying that day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must quickly go to the-- to the border crossing and away from the SS, if I may.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to give another vote of thanks to the warm-- when we crossed out of, out of Germany, that was one thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had a little no-man's land, and then immediately you're in Holland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- my vote of thanks goes to the wonderfully warm-hearted ladies of the, of the-- I don't know what they were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know the organization, the Jewish organization, in Holland-- that were waiting for us, that streamed through the corridors, hugging everybody, handing out cups of cocoa-- great touch, cocoa!",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Hot chocolate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, I mean, it was-- and that's when many children broke down and really cried, that's when the let themselves.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because you don't want to let yourself, before the others, and before you really know that you're out, because you don't want to break down for nothing.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
